<div class=profile><center> ----!! WARNING! SONIC ADVENTURE 2 SPOILERS AHEAD! PROCEED WITH CAUTION! THANK YOU !!---- </center>

<p>The original concept for the ultimate life form was a creature who would open the doors for a better world.  That is until Prof. Gerald Robotnik went insane with rage, and created the true ultimate life-form, Codename: Shadow, to bring fear and destruction to the people of Earth.

<p>Finally freed from the military base 50 years later by the one, the only, Dr. Eggman (grandson of Gerald), Shadow wasted no time in carrying out the wishes of his creator, and had all of the Chaos Emeralds brought aboard the Space Colonly ARK to power the Eclipse Cannon, which he promised the mad doctor he could use to take over the world.

<p>One very important ability given to this hedgehog is Chaos Control.  By using this method, allowing him to warp time and space and instantly transport from one place to another, is what truely makes him the ultimate lifeform.  That is, until he learned that another hedgehog had mastered the trick, and had equaled him in power.  With the power of the seven Chaos Emeralds, Shadow becomes Super Shadow.  Super Shadow is invincible, and just as strong as Super Sonic.

<p>Though Shadow is a wee bit wound up in himself with being the "ultimate lifeform" and all, he does have and ooey gooey caramel center inside.  Shadow has memories of a mysterious girl named "Maria".  The young, crippled girl was one of his only friends aboard the space colony ARK.  Before being sent to Earth, he made a promise to her:  to make every human on Earth happy.  Shadow lived up to this promise by helping to defeat Biolizard (prototype of the ultimate lifeform) aboard the ARK and preventing the space colony from colliding with the Earth by using Chaos Control to transport it back into orbit around the planet.  In doing so, Shadow sacrificed his own life, just to keep his promise.</div><br>
   </font></b></td></tr>
